headline: 5 Insurers Poised to Outperform Estimates This Earnings Season
summary: Better pricing, exposure growth, accelerated digitalization and sturdy capital are expected to help BRK.B, MET, LNC, WTW and AFL outperform third-quarter earnings estimates.

headline: Exploring Analyst Estimates for MetLife (MET) Q3 Earnings, Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Besides Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimates for MetLife (MET), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended September 2024.
